# Forecasting - Fall 2018

This package is intended as a support for the Forecasting class
taught at the University of Lausanne in Fall 2018 
(check the course website [here](https://fc2018.netlify.com/))

This package will be updated quite often, make sure you have the last version.

To install the package:
```R
# If not installed, first install 'devtools'
install.packages("devtools")

# Install the package
devtools::install_github("SMAC-Group/fc2018")
```
